Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Biologically Active Chalcones in 1,4-Dioxane and N,N-Dimethyl Formamide from (298.15 to 318.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of some chalcones in 1,4-dioxane and N,N-dimethyl formamide were measured by a gravimetrical method from (298.15 to 318.15) K under atmospheric pressure, and the solubility data were correlated against temperature.
